<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Confirme seu e-mail</title>

  <!-- Font Awesome (ícones) -->
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
  />

  <!-- Fonte Inter -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0D1222;
      --panel: #161B30;
      --card: #1A1F3A;
      --border: #373E59;
      --text: #FFFFFF;
      --muted: #AAB0D9;
      --primary: #6C64EF;
      --primary-hover: #8B5CF6;
      --danger: #E54848;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #151a3a, var(--bg));
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    .topbar {
      background: rgba(22, 27, 48, 0.9);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      padding: 16px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .brand i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .back-link {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* MAIN */
    .wrap {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* ALERT */
    .alert {
      margin: 24px auto 0;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a1020, #3b1425);
      border: 1px solid var(--danger);
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .alert i {
      color: var(--danger);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .alert .title {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .alert .desc {
      color: #ffd7d7;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* CARD */
    .card {
      margin: 60px auto;
      max-width: 560px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #181f3d, #12172e);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 34px 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, .35);
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 22px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .card h2 i {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    /* BUTTONS */
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #1e2447;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: .2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-hover));
      border: none;
    }

    .btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
      filter: brightness(1.15);
    }

    /* MOBILE */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .card {
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding: 28px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="brand">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i>
      <span>Zapconnect</span>
    </div>

    <a class="back-link" href="/login">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Voltar
    </a>
  </header>

  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="alert">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
      <div>
        <div class="title">Acesso bloqueado</div>
        <div class="desc">
          Você precisa confirmar seu e-mail para continuar usando o sistema.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-circle-check"></i>
        Confirme seu e-mail
      </h2>

      <p>
        Antes de acessar o Zapconnect, você precisa confirmar seu e-mail.
      </p>

      <p>
        Verifique sua caixa de entrada (ou spam) e clique no link enviado.
      </p>

      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i>
        Sair
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
